Package: data.gov
Title: Data.gov Federal Open Data Catalog (CKAN) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Data.gov CKAN API covering dataset
